**[[[A History of Reaction]]]:** Information retrieval specialists have attempted in this archive to provide the clearest possible history of POI-1844. Certain events described in this document may be presented out of order, or in contradictory ways. This does not mean they did not happen. //by TyGently//

**[[[SCP-3475|SCP-3475 - Our Shifting Foundations]]]:** If each of these initiatives can be thought of as exerting a force on civilian humanity, SCP-3475 is the sum of these forces: a single vector denoting the direction in which human thought is being changed. //by TyGently//

**[[[SCP-7890]]]:** ‚Ä¶the Puebla Cartel has developed a bespoke manufacturing process taking advantage of the inherently large EVE output of human sacrifice (utilizing enhanced Nordic pagan rituals) as a crude replacement. //by Anorrack//

